name: Like the old day
description:
Remember what its feel when you were young? this piece of work will take back to the old day that you still young. when we look outdside through the window while the car still driving its just a satisfice feeling. we dont even know where it gonna take us to or somehow you know, but seem not to care about. its feel so very fucking good when we look outside and see the cloud, car, building light, electric pole, lamp keep moving pass in front of our eyes. like everything no matter any more. like when we were young, like the yesterday, like the long day.

Like the old day. Enjoy

welp this only 10 piece not more, not less.
